Bushido Burrito on GitHub

About
---

This is a collection of demos by Jason Estey for a variety of platforms and
primarily demonstrating game programming related ideas.  It is very much a
work in progress and is intended to demonstrate a variety of nifty tricks.
There are also major contributions by some of Jason's friends.

More of Jason's work can be found at http://bushidoburrito.com/


Contents
---

Programs are loosely organized by platform.


Git Tips
---

Some good stuff to know about Git:

- Always use "git config --global core.autoclrf true"


